---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Contact | Michael Charles Portfolio">
  <section class="contact-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>

    <h1>Get in touch</h1>

    <p>
      This portfolio is intended as an explorable view of my professional
      experience, technical interests, and current development areas.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you would like to discuss a role, project, collaboration, or simply want
      to know more about any of the work shown here, please get in touch.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-card">
      <h2>Contact details</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Email: <span>add-email-address-here</span></li>
        <li>LinkedIn: <span>add-linkedin-url-here</span></li>
        <li>GitHub: <span>add-github-url-here</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-card">
      <h2>Useful context</h2>

      <p>
        I am particularly interested in technical project delivery, data-led
        transformation, cybersecurity, software development, and roles that sit
        between technical teams, business needs, and long-term product thinking.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #93c5fd;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #f8fafc;
    font-size: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #bfdbfe;
  }

  p,
  li {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-card {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #111827;
  }

  span {
    color: #94a3b8;
  }
</style>